"{\"uid\": \"foxsports.com-live-blog-olympics-2024-paris-olympics-live-updates-top-moments-from-opening-ceremony\", \"text\": \"POPULAR SEARCHES  BROWSE BY  The 2024 Paris Olympics kicked off Friday as athletes representing over 200 nations paraded in boats down the Seine River during the opening ceremony, marking the first ceremony held outside a stadium.  The Games, which consist of 329 events spread among 32 different sports, continue through Sunday, Aug. 11.  Here are the highlights!\"}"